---
title: Asian Carrot & Corn Fritters with Kumara Sesame Salad & Soy Aioli
description: Keep your eyes on your fritters when this meal hits the table because with the incredibly tasty combo of veggies, Thai spices and
soy aioli they're ripe for the thieving!

*"Keep an eye out...Due to recent sourcing challenges, we’ve replaced radish with pear, which may be a little different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!"*

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
